{"tid":2179804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國安法實施 銀行需配合警方","createTime":"2020-08-29T11:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T15:14:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e924bbb47bd9eeed113a6d08da5c61fd619111db","tid":2179804,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200829/E6QFYRO3VRDL3NKKUF25SPM4U4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200829%2FE6QFYRO3VRDL3NKKUF25SPM4U4%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=6884f937\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200829%2FE6QFYRO3VRDL3NKKUF25SPM4U4%2F&h=4390830a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200829/E6QFYRO3VRDL3NKKUF25SPM4U4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國安法實施 銀行需配合警方<br />\n<br />\n■因應《港區國安法》實施，金管局前日聯同警方與銀行界高層舉行交流會。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】因應《港區國安法》實施，執法過程與銀行合規操作可能潛在問題，金管局前日聯同警方與銀行界高層舉行交流會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金管局應制訂指引<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，會面內容其一重點，提及《國安法》生效後賦予作為執法機關的警務處更大權力，在特殊情況下作出搜查、或要求銀行凍結以至充公涉嫌干犯法例人士的戶口資產等行動時，警方毋須事先持有法庭有關頒令，銀行需按警方要求相應配合。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，警方亦在交流會指出，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄認為，金管局應就銀行如被執法部門要求，就涉嫌牴觸《國安法》人士戶口凍結資產，應如何處理制訂指引，以確保各行做法統一及不會對客戶造成不公平情況。<br />\n<br />\n金管局發言人前日回覆說，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c167033ec83ae82774faf949e06e427289bfe4a9","tid":2179804,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c657cad51836710f0acfbd940faafc157e693c4","tid":2179804,"uid":246371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:36:15.000Z","msg":"GG玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1d3ee7944f78b16d59ab671bba06234ccc130d","tid":2179804,"uid":17443,"like":4,"disl